The main campus of the '''University of Sopron''' ([[:hu:Soproni_Egyetem|Soproni Egyetem]], abbreviated SOE) is located in [[Sopron]], Hungary.
The school traces its roots to 1735.<ref name="history1">[http://www.uniwest.hu/index.php/2362/?&L=4 The History of the University], uniwest.hu, Retrieved 15 October 2015</ref>
